      72.0,
      49.44,
      420.75,
      73.44
    ],
    "text": "2.1 Introduction of business and businessman",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      18.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      89.24,
      471.02,
      139.01
    ],
    "text": "It is not necessary to explain about businesses.That is because we deal with businesses all the time. Think of goods and services we consume to fulfill our day to day needs and wants in the following contexts.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      159.34,
      166.0,
      175.41
    ],
    "text": "Example :-",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldItal",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      178.64,
      286.35,
      194.4
    ],
    "text": "Wash yourself in the morning",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      197.63,
      227.96,
      213.4
    ],
    "text": "Have a cup of tea",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      216.63,
      241.64,
      232.4
    ],
    "text": "Prepare daily meals",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      235.62,
      224.03,
      251.39
    ],
    "text": "Watch television",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      254.62,
      320.98,
      270.39
    ],
    "text": "Get ready to go to school or to work",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      285.02,
      471.03,
      364.77
    ],
    "text": "We need to consume a variety of goods and services for the above activities. Think about the complexity of processes from producing goods and services by different institutions and people to fulfil human needs. All the production and distribution of goods and services are done by businesses. Now we can identify what businesses are.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      379.4,
      471.02,
      427.16
    ],
    "text": "Business refers to all the activities related to production and distribution of goods and services to fulfil human needs and wants. The people who carry out these activities are called businessmen.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      452.64,
      231.7,
      476.64
    ],
    "text": "2.2 Needs and Wants",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      18.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      494.44,
      471.01,
      542.2
    ],
    "text": "The basic things which are essential in order to live are known as needs. The various ways by which the needs are fulfilled are called wants. Each want is created on a need. Accordingly, needs are fulfilled by satisfying wants.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
